910. CMAJ Open. 2021 Apr 22;9(2):E443-E450. doi: 10.9778/cmajo.20200154. Print
2021  Apr-Jun.

The cost-effectiveness of adding tomosynthesis to mammography-based breast 
cancer screening: an economic analysis.

Cressman S(1), Mar C(2), Sam J(2), Kan L(2), Lohrisch C(2), Spinelli JJ(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Integrative Oncology (Cressman), BC Cancer Research Centre, 
Vancouver, BC; Faculty of Health Sciences (Cressman), Simon Fraser University, 
Burnaby, BC; Cancer Screening (Mar, Sam, Kan), BC Cancer; Department of 
